&gt;&gt; Elise Friedland: Thank
you so much, Michael,

00:02:28.550 --> 00:02:30.330
and thank you for
this opportunity.

00:02:30.330 --> 00:02:32.180
Thank you all for coming.

00:02:32.180 --> 00:02:36.940
I'm delighted to be here and
Michael did a pretty good job

00:02:36.940 --> 00:02:41.550
of giving you some background
but I just needed to go

00:02:41.550 --> 00:02:44.520
through some thank yous
