My own institution also supplied
some funding for this so got

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:30.150
to give GW a little shout out.

00:03:30.150 --> 00:03:34.010
But also, there was an
entire team from the Library

00:03:34.010 --> 00:03:37.520
of Congress who has been
