00:42:18.090 --> 00:42:20.810
Oh boy, anybody got
any leads over there?

00:42:20.810 --> 00:42:26.010
But you can read the discussions
about acquisitions and what

00:42:26.010 --> 00:42:31.000
to spend your money on and so
that I also want to follow up on

00:42:31.000 --> 00:42:35.260
because I'm fascinated
by how they thought

00:42:35.260 --> 00:42:37.360
to acquire these volumes.

00:42:37.360 --> 00:42:39.240
And I've been looking
at the catalogues

00:42:39.240 --> 00:42:41.460
