yet in 1849.

00:43:04.930 --> 00:43:08.000
But I might look to see if
we purchased that in 1854

00:43:08.000 --> 00:43:10.010
or shortly thereafter
when it came out,

00:43:10.010 --> 00:43:11.530
whether, you know, they.

00:43:11.530 --> 00:43:15.410
But the question is, why
did they pick these volumes

00:43:15.410 --> 00:43:18.800
as opposed to Francois Masois,
as opposed to somebody else?

00:43:18.800 --> 00:43:22.530
It's interesting so that's
another thing that I want

00:43:22.530 --> 00:43:25.590
